title: WatchFaceOne for ZenWatch 2 (Unreleased)
summary: A simple analog watch face designed for ASUS ZenWatch 2.
description: Simple black background watch face designed for ZenWatch 2.Date may now be visible in low bit ambient mode (white - due to low bit ambient mode on zenwatch 2) and return to red when leaving ambient mode.
